sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant R as API Route (/api/articles POST)
    participant S as ArticleService
    participant Repo as ArticleRepository
    participant DB as Database

    C->>R: POST /api/articles<br>{title, content}
    R->>S: create_article(title, content, current_user)
    S->>Repo: create_article(article_data)
    Repo->>DB: Insert article document
    DB-->>Repo: Return inserted_id
    Repo-->>S: Return article_id
    S-->>R: {"message": "Article created successfully",<br>"article_id": article_id}
    R-->>C: 201 Created<br>JSON response
